        </a>
        <a href="/blog/pocket-doors-vs-regular-doors" class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-border/30 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow block">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg tracking-wide text-primary mb-2">Pocket Doors vs Regular Doors</h3>
